    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Could you get a bit more specific with the grooming part? Like, when it comes to hair and makeup, what are some specific styles or looks that really help convey that sense of \"polished and disciplined\" you mentioned? I want to make sure the guidance is really concrete for the employees.",
